  <div class="columns large-6" style="padding-top: 20px">

        <h2>Welcome to Summit Pacific College</h2>
        <p><b>Thank-you for your interest in Summit Pacific College</b></p>
        <p>We hope that your visit here will answer some of your questions as you consider a course of study that is right for you. Whether you are interested in pastoral ministry, counselling, missions and cross-cultural communication, theology, worship arts, music or our one-year Omega program, you'll discover we've designed programs that will equip you to excel  in your chosen calling.</p>
    
   
  </div>
  <!-- end .columns.large-6 --> 
</div>
<!-- end .row -->
<div class="row add-bottom">
  <div class="columns large-6">
    <h5 class="alt"><span>PROGRAMS</span></h5>
    <div class="section-container accordion" data-section="accordion">
      <section>
        <h5 class="title" data-section-title="data-section-title"><a href="#"><em class="icon-plus-sign"></em><em class="icon-minus-sign"></em> School of Graduate Studies</a></h5>
        <div class="content" data-section-content="data-section-content">
          <a href="https://www.summitpacific.ca/graduatestudies/index.php"><p>Summit Pacific College's School of Graduate Studies offers graduate-level theological education that is flexible and affordable.</strong> Our program is focused on, but is not limited to, theological and biblical perspectives within the modern Pentecostal movement. Thus our individual courses are related to Pentecostal issues and praxis in various areas such as biblical studies, hermeneutics, history and homiletics. <strong>Learn More <em class="icon-chevron-right"> </em></strong></p></a>
        </div>
      </section>
    
    <section>
        <h5 class="title" data-section-title="data-section-title"><a href="#"><em class="icon-plus-sign"></em><em class="icon-minus-sign"></em> Biblical Theology</a></h5>
        <div class="content" data-section-content="data-section-content">
          <a href="https://www.summitpacific.ca/programs/btheology.php"><p>This program is designed to give the student a well rounded college education with a sound preparation in Bible and Theology, Biblical language emphasis, as well as a foundation in Practical Studies and General Education. <strong>Learn More <em class="icon-chevron-right"> </em></strong></p></a>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section>
        <h5 class="title" data-section-title="data-section-title"><a href="#"><em class="icon-plus-sign"></em><em class="icon-minus-sign"></em> Church Ministries</a></h5>
        <div class="content" data-section-content="data-section-content">
          <a href="https://www.summitpacific.ca/programs/cministries.php"><p>This program is of particular interest to those who wish to stress education and teaching as primary aspects of their Christian ministry. It provides an in-depth study of Bible and Theology, Practical Studies concerned with teaching and learning methods and General Studies which prepare students for effective communication of their message and convictions.  <strong>Learn More <em class="icon-chevron-right"> </em></strong></p></a>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section>
        <h5 class="title" data-section-title="data-section-title"><a href="#"><em class="icon-plus-sign"></em><em class="icon-minus-sign"></em> Counselling Foundations</a></h5>
        <div class="content" data-section-content="data-section-content">
          <a href="https://www.summitpacific.ca/programs/counselling.php"><p>Rooted in a firm foundation of Bible and Theology, the Counselling Foundations program is designed to equip the student with basic counselling skills for lay counselling and pastoral counselling situations. This program is also intended to provide students with the foundations and prerequisites for future studies in counselling at a graduate level. <strong>Learn More <em class="icon-angle-right"></em></strong></p></a>
        </div>
      </section>
            <section>
        <h5 class="title" data-section-title="data-section-title"><a href="#"><em class="icon-plus-sign"></em><em class="icon-minus-sign"></em> General Studies</a></h5>
        <div class="content" data-section-content="data-section-content">
          <a href="https://www.summitpacific.ca/programs/twu.php"><p>This is a combined program for those students who desire a rigorous program of education that forms a strong Christian Worldview from solid Biblical, Theological, and General Arts studies.  <strong>Learn More <em class="icon-angle-right"></em></strong></p></a>
        </div>
      </section>
            <section>
        <h5 class="title" data-section-title="data-section-title"><a href="#"><em class="icon-plus-sign"></em><em class="icon-minus-sign"></em> Intercultural Studies</a></h5>
        <div class="content" data-section-content="data-section-content">
          <a href="https://www.summitpacific.ca/programs/intercult.php"><p>The Intercultural Studies program is designed to provide the student with a solid grounding in Bible and theology, Practical cross-cultural ministry and General Studies. With an emphasis on intercultural ministry, the program imparts principles that will assist the student to effectively communicate the gospel across cultural barriers.  <strong>Learn More <em class="icon-angle-right"></em></strong></p></a>
        </div>
      </section>
            <section>
        <h5 class="title" data-section-title="data-section-title"><a href="#"><em class="icon-plus-sign"></em><em class="icon-minus-sign"></em> Music Leadership</a></h5>
        <div class="content" data-section-content="data-section-content">
          <a href="https://www.summitpacific.ca/programs/music.php"><p>The Music Leadership prepares and equips  students for worship ministry in local church contexts to provide effective pastoral leadership. Together with the foundational study of Bible and Theology, Practics, General Studies, the student is provided with important foundations in corporate worship ministry training.  <strong>Learn More <em class="icon-angle-right"></em></strong></p></a>
        </div>
      </section>
            <section>
        <h5 class="title" data-section-title="data-section-title"><a href="#"><em class="icon-plus-sign"></em><em class="icon-minus-sign"></em> Not For Profit Organizational Leadership</a></h5>
        <div class="content" data-section-content="data-section-content">
          <a href="https://www.summitpacific.ca/programs/nfpleadership.php"><p>This program is designed for those who want to serve in areas of institutional leadership. The program&#39;s focus is on leadership principles for work in non-profit organizations, churches, Non-Governmental Organizations, or foreign mission contexts. As a four year BA program it aims to provide a holistic preparation for a leadership career in administration that is shaped by Biblical and Theological study, practical course work, and grounded in General Studies. <strong>Learn More <em class="icon-angle-right"></em></strong></p></a>
        </div>
      </section>
            <section>
        <h5 class="title" data-section-title="data-section-title"><a href="#"><em class="icon-plus-sign"></em><em class="icon-minus-sign"></em> Omega Global</a></h5>
        <div class="content" data-section-content="data-section-content">
          <a href="https://www.summitpacific.ca/programs/omegaglobal.php"><p>OMEGA Global is a response to those students who desire a one-year program that emphasizes relational discipleship and practical ministry opportunities. The goal of the OMEGA program is to develop Christian character through academic learning and hands on ministry experience. OMEGA includes a 3 - 4 week overseas missions experience. <strong>Learn More <em class="icon-angle-right"></em></strong></p></a>
        </div>
      </section>
                  <section>
        <h5 class="title" data-section-title="data-section-title"><a href="#"><em class="icon-plus-sign"></em><em class="icon-minus-sign"></em> RoMER Certificate</a></h5>
        <div class="content" data-section-content="data-section-content">
          <a href="https://www.summitpacific.ca/programs/romer.php"><p>The college offers courses that specifically fulfill the PAOC's Recognition of Ministry Credential. The Recognition of Ministry Education Requirements Certificate (RoMER) fulfills the academic requirements of this credential and is attainable in one year. <strong>Learn More <em class="icon-angle-right"></em></strong></p></a>
        </div>
      </section>
                  <section>
        <h5 class="title" data-section-title="data-section-title"><a href="#"><em class="icon-plus-sign"></em><em class="icon-minus-sign"></em> Sound Production &amp; Media</a></h5>
        <div class="content" data-section-content="data-section-content">
          <a href="https://www.summitpacific.ca/programs/recording.php"><p>This one-year program equips students with skills for sound production, recording, media, and church ministry. It provides an excellent foundation for service in church audio & media departments. <strong>Learn More <em class="icon-angle-right"></em></strong></p></a>
        </div>
      </section>
            <section>
        <h5 class="title" data-section-title="data-section-title"><a href="#"><em class="icon-plus-sign"></em><em class="icon-minus-sign"></em> Pastoral Theology</a></h5>
        <div class="content" data-section-content="data-section-content">
          <a href="https://www.summitpacific.ca/programs/ptheology.php"><p>This program is designed for students who sense God&#39;s call to pastor an existing local church or plant a new one. The Pastoral Theology program supplies a solid foundation in Bible and Theology, introductory courses in General Studies and instruction in the skills required of a pastor. This program includes individual and group mentoring. <strong>Learn More <em class="icon-angle-right"></em></strong></p></a>
        </div>
      </section>
            <section>
        <h5 class="title" data-section-title="data-section-title"><a href="#"><em class="icon-plus-sign"></em><em class="icon-minus-sign"></em> Youth Leadership</a></h5>
        <div class="content" data-section-content="data-section-content">
          <a href="https://www.summitpacific.ca/programs/youth.php"><p>This program is designed for students who will begin pastoral ministry as youth pastors. The program meets the standards of the Pentecostal Assemblies of Canada for ordination. It consists of Bible and Theology, Practics Studies and General Studies. Included in the Practics Studies is a youth leadership major of 24 semester hours. <strong>Learn More <em class="icon-angle-right"></em></strong></p></a>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
  <!-- end .columns.large-3 -->
