    <h5 class="alt"><span>News and Events</span></h5>

  <div class="boxen">
   <div class="news-details" style="height: 600px; overflow-y: scroll;">
   				<p><em class="icon-chevron-right"></em> <strong>Summit Pacific College welcomes applications for the following positions: Pastoral Theology Director and Admissions/Recruitment Counselor - <a href="https://www.summitpacific.ca/contact/employment.php">Click Here For More Information</a></p>
   				
   				<p><em class="icon-chevron-right"></em> <strong>Registration is now open for the School of Graduate Studies Spring Module</strong> <b><i>Pentecostal Preaching in a Post-Christian Culture: The Power of Imagination to Transform Lives</i></b> March 7, 10-11, 2016 taught by Dr. Mick Nelson.  <a href="https://www.summitpacific.ca/graduatestudies/current.php" target="_blank"> Course Information, fees and registration.</a></p>
   				
   				<p><em class="icon-chevron-right"></em> <strong>Visit the President's weekly blog</strong></p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://blogs.summitpacific.ca/lead/" title="from Dave's Desk" target="_blank"><img src="https://www.summitpacific.ca/about/images/davesdesksmall.jpg" alt="from Dave's Desk"  style="border: none" /><br /><b><i>from Dave's Desk</i></b> - this week "Emerging Leader"</a></p>
   
   				<p><em class="icon-chevron-right"></em> <strong>School of Graduate Studies</strong> We are pleased to announce that the new Dean of Graduate Studies at Summit Pacific College is Dr. Riku Tuppurainen. We will be offering a Graduate certificate for 5 courses taught from a distinctively Pentecostal perspective (Hermeneutics, Pastoral Theology, History of Pentecostalism, Homiletics and Studies in Lucan Theology). We are also pleased to report that these courses are fully transferable into the Master of Arts in Ministerial Leadership degree offered by Southeastern University (Lakeland, Florida) affiliated with the Assemblies of God.  <a href="https://www.summitpacific.ca/events/pdf/School_of_Graduate_Studies.pdf" target="_blank">Read more (pdf)</a> | <a href="https://www.summitpacific.ca/events/index.php" target="_blank">Read more (News & Events Page)</a></p>
   				
   				<p><em class="icon-chevron-right"></em> <strong>MUSIC & SOUND PRODUCTION DEVELOPMENTS - BA in Music Leadership!</strong> Our new major in Music Leadership will provide students an opportunity to develop their music knowledge and competency on a chosen instrument.  It will emphasize the development of team dynamics, performance skills, and volunteer management.  Components of sound production, media and stage design are important aspects of the program.  <a href="https://www.summitpacific.ca/events/index.php">Read more</a></p> 
                
                <p><em class="icon-chevron-right"></em> <strong>More15 Workshops -</strong> MORE15 Workshop recordings are now available. In fact all of the MORE15 audio is available for you to experience. <a href="https://www.summitpacific.ca/more15media/index.php"> Click go there</a></p>
                
